# Extends Flux source-controller's default ignore rules. The defaults strip
# image/binary extensions (*.png, *.jpg, *.gif, ...) from the build artifact to
# keep it small — which also drops legitimate assets that a kustomization needs.
# Re-include (negate) the authentik brand images, which a kustomize
# configMapGenerator reads to build the authentik-brand-assets ConfigMap served
# by the brand-assets nginx deployment.
!kubernetes/infrastructure/authentik/brand-assets/*.png
!kubernetes/infrastructure/authentik/brand-assets/*.webp
